dropped over the last three years from $34 to $21 per month on average for Lilly insulins. That's quite a bit lower than our competitors. But that does hit the price line for us, either through the now 70% off insulin lispro product, which is available, or through the buy-downs we do at the point of sale to $35 per month. So that's in the background.

There is sort of a terminal quantity to that but we have seen good adoption. And I guess, the good news is patients are taking advantage of that and it's showing up and retaining volume. It does hit the net price line though.

