So you will see kind of the evolution of any retail product to be a higher net price at the beginning of the life cycle. And then, as the lower -- if you reach volume in lower-priced segments, you'll see that decline like we've talked about over -- with Trulicity over the last couple of years. Now we will have extensive patient support programs in the first six months for tirzepatide. So again, I wouldn't be looking too much at that for tirzepatide in the first six months.

